				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I often get a problem on one of my pc's.  The character has alot of trouble moving, this happens mainly in zones with lots of "trees" or moving objects, aka PoK...  
<br />

<br />
Anyway, I usually hit Alt + Enter key, to switch to windows mode, then after a few seconds Alt + Enter back to normal mode, if this does not fix, i usually hit F9, pop up the map, and move around like that, when Im at my destionation, say Big Bank, I will go F9 to the desired view...
<br />

<br />
Bit of a painful way, but tends to help if you have a machine that is not really up to spec.
<br />

<br />
Hope it helps you.
<br />

